headline: Parnassus Growth Equity Fund Sold Charter Communications (CHTR) Due To Stronger-Than-Anticipated Competition
summary: Parnassus Investments, an investment management company, released the “Parnassus Growth Equity Fund” third quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the third quarter, the Fund (Investor Shares) returned 3.29% (net of fees) outperforming the Russell 1000 Growth Index’s 3.19% gain. Stock selection in the Health Care sector primarily […]
